 Galvatron looked as the map beeped. "Hold it Cyngar. Megatron's oreds are 
moving out." He sent a comm to Nightshade and quilldart. "You two meet us 10  
 miles  outside the tripred base. Things gave come up." He turned back to 
Cyngar. "I have people in place who will make this battle interesting. By 
taking out megatron quickly we will destroy a major threat. While the bots 
are distracted with eachother we can attack Megs himself and end this. I will 
do that personaly. " The shields would go up with the auto denfenses until 
Galvatron disabled them.

-Quilldart stopped. "Damn I hate it when he does that. Lets go nightshade." 
He turns towrds the point they were set to meet.
